    - Hey doofus, I'm speaking to you. #04
    - Am I talking to a wall right now? #05
    - Hey {player_name}, I'm not talking to myself you know! #06
    - Answer me, {player_name}! #07
    - Are you even listening? #08
}

->->

+[timeout] -> Yuki_Timeout

